<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> the place on which the memorial lies through [ . . .  ] written [on the] sarcophagus to be destroyed, both himself <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> nor women to give birth naturally nor [ . . . all his race and [from] sacred altars <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/></p>
</div>
<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>Elements from a particularly extensive funerary curse.</p>
